title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 14 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 14 2022
description:
Despicable: 69-year-old cancer patient grandma to be jailed for Jan. 6th trespassing. Mr. New York, Mark Simone of WOR, joins Clay and Buck to talk about crime in the Big Apple. It's National Mac & Cheese Day. A 24/7 VIP calls out Buck on In-N-Out fries.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
